history.content:
Interested in learning more about quant trading at one of the world’s most successful market making firms? You are invited to apply to the Citadel Securities in-person trading challenge!

During our live trading competition, you will work with team members to solve the types of problems we face every day. Winning team members are eligible for generous prizes. Food and swag coupons will be provided to all attendees.

Next Steps: Please apply with your most up to date resume here. If you are chosen to participate, a member of our team will provide location details. Space is limited!

Application Deadline: Friday October 8
